    "Specifically, GNN-RAG+RA outperforms RoG by 5.0-6.1% points at Hit, while it outperforms or matches ToG+GPT-4 performance, using an LLM with only 7B parameters and much fewer LLM calls, while GNN-RAG can be deployed on a single 24GB GPU.",
